snippet.title: Pledge of Love | Otome Game PV
snippet.description:
You missed sorority rush week, but don’t worry — there’s still an opening… at an all-boys fraternity! But can you be convincing as one of the boys…?
Download 'Pledge of Love' to find out! 

Available on Google Play or Otomania for iOS. Check it out from the links below!

Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.genius.fraternityotome

Apple:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/otomania/id1503465177


Lyrics: Ryuuzaki Hajime
Composition: Ryuuzaki Hajime
Artist name: Losstime Life
Vocals: Shirai Mai
